OL,3,CReform UK threatens to scrap #30m of
OL,4,CBangor University funding if elected
OL,6,FA leading Reform UK politician has
OL,7,Fthreatened to cut #30m of funding for
OL,8,Fa Welsh university if the party is
OL,9,Felected after two MPs were blocked
OL,10,Ffrom hosting a Q&A.
OL,12,FBangor University's Debating and
OL,13,FPolitical society says it was
OL,14,Fapproached by Reform MPs Jack Anderton
OL,15,Fand Sarah Pochin to host a Q&A with
OL,16,Fstudents but the society declined the
OL,17,Foffer in line with their "values".
