OL,6,FMr Yusuf said: "Bangor University have
OL,7,Fbanned Reform and called us 'racist,
OL,8,Ftransphobic and homophobic'.
OL,10,F"Bangor receives #30 million in state
OL,11,Ffunding a year, much of which comes
OL,12,Ffrom Reform-voting taxpayers. (sic) am
OL,13,Fsure they won't mind losing every
OL,14,Fpenny of that state funding under a
OL,15,FReform government. After all, they
OL,16,Fwouldn't want a racist's money would
OL,17,Fthey?"
