OL,3,CReform UK threatens to scrap #30m of
OL,4,CBangor University funding if elected
OL,6,FThe debating society said it had made
OL,7,Fthe decision not to host the Q&A in
OL,8,Fline with their "values" and implored
OL,9,Fother societies to follow suit "in
OL,10,Fkeeping hate out of our universities."
OL,12,FThe full statement read: "The Debating
OL,13,Fand Political Society received a
OL,14,Frequest from Jack Anderton and Sarah
OL,15,FPochin MP of Reform UK to attend
OL,16,FBangor University and give a Q&A to
OL,17,Fstudents. In line with our values,
OL,18,Fthis request was refused.
