OL,3,CReform UK threatens to scrap #30m of
OL,4,CBangor University funding if elected
OL,6,F"We stand by this decision as a
OL,7,Fcommittee. We have zero tolerance for
OL,8,Fany form of racism, transphobia, or
OL,9,Fhomophobia displayed by the members of
OL,10,FReform UK. Their approach to the lives
OL,11,Fof others is antithetical to the
OL,12,Fvalues of welcoming and fair debate
OL,13,Fthat our society has upheld for 177
OL,14,Fyears.
OL,16,FThe statement continued: "We are proud
OL,17,Fto be the first of the debating unions
OL,18,Fto take a stand against Reform UK. We
OL,19,Fstrongly implore our fellow societies
OL,20,Fto join us in keeping hate out of our
OL,21,Funiversities."
