OL,6,FBangor University says the views of
OL,7,Fthe society are their own and do not
OL,8,Freflect the university policy as a
OL,9,Fwhole.
OL,11,FA spokesperson for the university
OL,12,Fsaid: "The social media post was
OL,13,Fissued by a student society and not by
OL,14,FBangor University. Student societies
OL,15,Fare created and run by students
OL,16,Fthrough the independent Students'
OL,17,FUnion.
