OL,3,CReform UK threatens to scrap #30m of
OL,4,CBangor University funding if elected
OL,6,F"The views expressed by societies are
OL,7,Ftheir own and do not reflect
OL,8,FUniversity policy. Bangor University
OL,9,Fremains politically neutral and
OL,10,Fsupports freedom of speech. Bangor
OL,11,FUniversity welcomes debate from across
OL,12,Fthe political spectrum."
OL,14,FReform UK did not confirm whether the
OL,15,Fparty echoed the statement issued on
OL,16,Fsocial media by Mr Yusuf but said
OL,17,F"universities should be a place of
OL,18,Ffree discussion."
