OL,3,CReform UK threatens to scrap #30m of
OL,4,CBangor University funding if elected
OL,6,FDan Thomas, Reform Wales Leader said:
OL,7,F"It's a sad state of affairs when a
OL,8,Funiversity debating society wants to
OL,9,Fde-platform a leading political party.
OL,11,F"Universities should be a place of
OL,12,Ffree discussion and engagement with
OL,13,Fdifferent ideas, but too often groups
OL,14,Fwithin universities want to wrap
OL,15,Fthemselves in cotton wool.
OL,17,F"We will safeguard free speech on
OL,18,Fcampus, and ensure basic liberties are
OL,19,Fprotected."
